{"tid":2353312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際或流亡的，國安法保障了其專利。其主張越近港泛民，越沒優勢","createTime":"2021-01-04T15:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T15:36:16.000Z","uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2895e82c46f1690e65de60740860e01a72ad1bec","tid":2353312,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:36:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158824287152357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158824287152357&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=5c06e22b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158824287152357</a><br />\n<br />\n國際，或者流亡的人，最大的優勢，是國安法威脅不到他們，他們會以及可以說國安法所禁止的言論與事。換句話說，如果新的更激進政治主張有市場的話，國安法的存在保障了他們的專利。反之，他們的主張與本地民主派越近，就越沒有優勢，因為他們離香港太遠，而且會越來越遠。"}]}